==English==
===Noun===
'''[[stage]] [[fright]]'''
#(''uncountable'') A state of [[nervousness]] about performing some action in front of a group of people, on or off of a stage; [[nerves]]; [[uncertainty]]; a lack of [[self-assurance]] before an audience.
#:''I did some guest-speaking at the middle school last year, and I experienced some '''stage fright''', before and during my first presentation.''